nodes.text: Prow was a type of blue alcoholic beverage. The drink notably had a bitter smell. In 22 BBY, undiluted prow was being served at the Outlander Club on the planet Coruscant and was kept in a tall tube on the counter behind the club's central bar. During the Clone Wars, Asajj Ventress requested prow at Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina on the desert planet Tatooine.
